			"styles": "\n\t/* :nth-child(An+B of S) where S is a bare An+B/number term (2n, 123) */\n\ta:nth-child(2n of 123) {\n\t\tcolor: red;\n\t}\n\n\ta:nth-child(2n of 2n) {\n\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t}\n\n\ta:nth-last-child(3 of 7) {\n\t\tcolor: green;\n\t}\n",
